<section class="py-24 sm:py-32 px-5 sm:px-8 section-divide">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-text-muted uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 reveal">The problem</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl italic leading-tight mb-6 reveal stagger-1">
      You kicked off three agents.<br/>Now you're stuck at your desk.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mb-16 reveal stagger-2">
      The interactions that matter are quick&mdash;15 seconds to check output, approve a change, redirect an agent. But you can't do them from anywhere else.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
      <!-- Pain 1 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border reveal stagger-3 group hover:border-border/80 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-red/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M13.875 18.825A10.05 10.05 0 0112 19c-4.478 0-8.268-2.943-9.543-7a9.97 9.97 0 011.563-3.029m5.858.908a3 3 0 114.243 4.243M9.878 9.878l4.242 4.242M3 3l18 18"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">You can't see the work</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Existing tools show you the conversation. You need to see the actual output&mdash;the code it wrote, the image it generated, the doc it updated. Without that, you're supervising blind.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 2 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border reveal stagger-4 group hover:border-border/80 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">You're waiting at your desk</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Your agent runs for 10 minutes, needs one "yes", then runs for 10 more. You're sitting there for 20 minutes of someone else's compute. You have better things to do.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain 3 -->
      <div class="p-6 rounded-xl bg-bg-card border border-border reveal stagger-5 group hover:border-border/80 transition-colors">
        <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Ideas strike away from screens</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">
          On a walk, on a run, cooking dinner. You want to spin up a new session, point it at a project, and let it run. Right now you have to go back to your laptop.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
